('chunk_c9263e4181552ced89','file_fddb398b50b775766b','00-IB-framework-reference.md','7. The 10 IB Learner Profile Attributes (the kind of person we grow)','Inquirers · Knowledgeable · Thinkers · Communicators · Principled · Open-minded · Caring · Risk-takers (Courageous) · Balanced · Reflective.

Name an attribute only when a task genuinely develops it (e.g., designing a fair experiment → *Principled* and *Inquirers*; presenting a viewpoint you disagree with → *Open-minded*).

